{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-express-disagreement/task-117","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-express-disagreement","challengeType":19,"description":"","nodules":null,"explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Maybe, but...</span> koristi se da priznaš nečiji argument, a zatim uvedeš drugačije gledište. Na primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Lily:</strong> <span class=\"highlighted-text\">We could move the meeting to the afternoon.</span></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Mark:</strong> <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Maybe, but some people might not be available then.</span> — Ova osoba priznaje mogućnost, ali ukazuje na potencijalni problem sa terminom.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>U tačnom odgovoru slažeš se da je fleksibilnost dobra, ali ističeš još jedan važan faktor koji treba uzeti u obzir.</p>\n</section>","helpCategory":"English","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte audio odgovor na pitanje ispod.</p>\n</section>","fields":{"slug":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-express-disagreement/task-117"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Razumete argument Anu, ali želite da uvedete drugačiju perspektivu. Šta biste mogli reći?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Maybe, but we also need to ensure everyone has the basic equipment to work remotely.</span></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":"EN4330daba"},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">I completely agree. Everyone should use their stipend however they want, with no guidelines.</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Kada Anna predlaže fleksibilnost, ne kaže da pravila uopšte ne treba da postoje.</p>","audioId":"ENb84491e7"}],"solution":1}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company1-boardroom.png","characters":[{"character":"Anna","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.2},"opacity":